      • getResponse

        private java.io.InputStream getResponse(org.apache.http.HttpRequest httpMethod)
                                 throws java.net.ConnectException
        This method perform request on server and return response from server. It also set status code. If during performing request is exception occur then AFSwinxConnectionException is thrown.
        Parameters:
        httpMethod - method which will be used.
        Returns:
        InputStream of response from server.
        Throws:
        java.net.ConnectException - if during request is exception occur.
